A man was found dead outside his home in Kanniagadu Road in Redcliffe near Verulam, KZN, on Monday morning. Reaction Unit South Africa (RUSA) said its members were called out to the scene at around 6 am, after a resident who was doing a wellness check in the area found the dead man. On arrival, reaction officers found a plastic dish filled with blood next to the man. The circumstances leading up to the manâ€™s death are uncertain at this point.